snippet.title: Evercade Interplay 'Collection 2' Cartridge Trailer
snippet.description:
Visit: http://evercade.co.uk/interplay-collection-2-cartridge/

The Interplay Collection 2 cartridge brings 7 more classic Interplay games to the Evercade, including: Earthworm Jim 2, Clayfighter 2, Claymates and more! The cartridge will be supplied in a stunning collectable retro style physical case.

Full games list:

1. Earthworm Jim 2
2. Clayfighter 2
3. The Adventures of Rad Gravity
4. Claymates
5. Prehistoric Man
6. The Brainies
7. Super Castles
